> -  duration.clock_type = GPR_TIMESPAN;

> +             GPR_MS_PER_SEC +
> +         (duration_pb->has_nanos ? duration_pb->nanos : 0) / GPR_NS_PER_MS;
>

> serverlist is valid. Rounding down is slightly more conservative.
